OL,5, A Brazilian woman has spoken of her    
OL,6, ordeal of being imprisoned - along with
OL,7, her two children - by her husband for  
OL,8, 17 years, local media report.          
OL,10,FThe family was rescued from a house in 
OL,11,Fthe Guaratiba neighbourhood, in the    
OL,12,Fwest of Rio de Janeiro on Thursday,    
OL,13,Fpolice said.                           
OL,15,FThe husband has been arrested.         
OL,17,FIn comments to authorities quoted by   
OL,18,FBrazilian news site G1, the woman      
OL,19,Falleged her husband had said she would 
OL,20,Fonly leave the house once she was dead.
